reviewText: A must have for all Sola Aoi fans! Great quality  video of her.
I've been in love with this woman from the first time I saw her.  Good, bad or indifferent I will continue to buy her movies.

This DVD video shows why Sola Aoi is so popular.  It captures her beauty and cuteness on camera.  This DVD is just her posing in front of the camera in her natural beauty.  The only complaint I have is the price.  But if you like beautiful asian women, this is good DVD to have in your collection.

I have a dvd called Raw Summer. Though there is no nudity in the movie, Sora Aoi is one beautiful girl to watch. If the price weren't so high for this DVD and others like it, I would have bought it a long time ago. Just too much $$ vs the time of film in the DVD.
